snippet.title: Mendel (Coming September 7th)
snippet.description:
Mendel is a science creativity sandbox about growing weird plants from alien genetics.

Coming September 7th to PC and Mac.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/899340/Mendel
Itch: https://owen-bell.itch.io/mendel

Trailer music by Chris Zabriskie http://chriszabriskie.com/
